{"type":"message","id":"49214f84","parentId":"dca3bf0f","timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:26:07.386Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the hooks directory has these entries:\n- HOOK.md (describes the hook system)\n- auto-score-classify/ (directory)\n- context-hook.js\n- handler.js (the bootstrap handler with self-improvement + session-summary)\n- handler.ts\n- on-command-error.sh\n- on-message.sh\n- self-improvement.js\n- session-summary/ (directory with its own handler.js)\n\nThe key question: is the `handler.js` (bootstrap hook) actually registered and firing? Let me check the hook registration mechanism.\n\nThe issue could be:\n1. The hook isn't registered in the gateway config\n2. The hook fires but the session-summary directory's hook creates the file after the bootstrap runs\n\n\n3. There's a timing issue where the bootstrap hook can't find a summary file because session-summary hasn't generated one yet from the previous session\n\nI need to verify how hooks get registered and whether they're actually loaded by the gateway.","thinkingSignature":"72a9a3d773db031a19962720c2187404d456dc49b662d398f8d7abb13044ab74"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1aad1f2f01ea4449a2bfa4bb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/config/models.json 2>/dev/null | head -30; echo \"---\"; cat ~/.openclaw/config/routing_rules.json 2>/dev/null | head -30"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_120a1b71cbc14acd9ae6f64a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ps aux | grep -E \"openclaw|gateway\" | grep -v grep | head -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":227,"output":288,"cacheRead":27520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28035,"cost":{"input":0.0000681,"output":0.0003456,"cacheRead":0.0016511999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0020648999999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776176759591,"responseId":"062d8177cb54200a1a4b0261cc8c7f57"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0f32f143","parentId":"49214f84","timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:26:07.502Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1aad1f2f01ea4449a2bfa4bb","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"version\": \"1.0\",\n  \"providers\": {\n    \"minimax\": {\n      \"type\": \"openai-compatible\",\n      \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.minimax.chat/v1\",\n      \"apiKey\": \"${MINIMAX_API_KEY}\"\n    },\n    \"deepseek\": {\n      \"type\": \"openai-compatible\",\n      \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.deepseek.com/v1\",\n      \"apiKey\": \"${DEEPSEEK_API_KEY}\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"models\": {\n    \"fast\": {\n      \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n      \"modelId\": \"minimax-m2.5\",\n      \"fallback\": \"deep\",\n      \"timeout\": 30000,\n      \"maxRetries\": 2\n    },\n    \"deep\": {\n      \"provider\": \"deepseek\",\n      \"modelId\": \"deepseek-chat\",\n      \"fallback\": \"fast\",\n      \"timeout\": 60000,\n      \"maxRetries\": 1\n    }\n  }\n---\n{\n  \"version\": \"1.0\",\n  \"rules\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"code_keywords\",\n      \"priority\": 100,\n      \"condition\": { \"contains\": [\"写代码\", \"编程\", \"重构\", \"debug\", \"脚本\", \"部署\", \"优化\", \"修复\", \"实现\"] },\n      \"target_agent\": \"fast_agent\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"deep_keywords\",\n      \"priority\": 100,\n      \"condition\": { \"contains\": [\"分析\", \"推理\", \"数学\", \"证明\", \"论文\", \"原理\"] },\n      \"target_agent\": \"deep_agent\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"classifier_task\",\n      \"priority\": 80,\n      \"condition\": { \"classifier_label\": [\"task_multi_step\", \"high_risk_automated\", \"fault_recovery\"] },\n      \"target_agent\": \"fast_agent\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"classifier_reasoning\",\n      \"priority\": 80,\n      \"condition\": { \"classifier_label\": [\"expert_user\", \"vague_request\"] },\n      \"target_agent\": \"deep_agent\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"fallback\",\n      \"priority\": 0,"}],"details":{"status":"comp