{"type":"message","id":"944ddb16","parentId":"60872937","timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:26:27.842Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the actual hooks configuration. All hooks are enabled:\n- session-memory ✅\n- command-logger ✅\n- self-improvement ✅\n- context_hook ✅\n- auto-score-classify ✅\n- session-summary ✅\n\nSo hooks are enabled. Let me check the gateway log to see if there are any errors, and also look at the session-summary hook's trigger conditions more carefully.\n\nThe key question: why didn't session-summary run this time?\n\nLet me check the session-summary hook handler more carefully and see if there's a trigger condition issue. Also check the gateway log.","thinkingSignature":"9bb7e4472b948717ccf5f8e444f45482c67f36017f9126e838b54479f36bb064"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1b31ff9d88ef4dc1a69482f3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/logs/commands.log 2>/dev/null | tail -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_069cc409b28a478599f941aa","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/handler.js 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":292,"output":194,"cacheRead":29440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29926,"cost":{"input":0.0000876,"output":0.0002328,"cacheRead":0.0017663999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0020867999999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776176781464,"responseId":"062d818d532c466ddf87722c29f67c71"}}
