{"type":"message","id":"29673b13","parentId":"42a3534b","timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:28:51.513Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2b3274672d704b4d8894f44a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"require('dotenv').config();\nconst fs = require('fs');\nconst path = require('path');\nconst express = require('express');\nconst http = require('http');\nconst axios = require('axios');\nconst WebSocket = require('ws');\nconst { createProxyMiddleware } = require('http-proxy-middleware');\nconst NodeCache = require('node-cache');\nconst { classify, score } = require('./clients/v8Client');\nconst { AIRouter } = require('@isaced/ai-router');\n\n// ==================== 配置加载 ====================\nconst HOME = process.env.HOME || '/home/ai';\nconst MODELS_CONFIG = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(path.join(HOME, '.openclaw/config/models.json')));\nconst RULES_CONFIG = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(path.join(HOME, '.openclaw/config/routing_rules.json')));\nconst OPENCLAW_CONFIG = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(path.join(HOME, '.openclaw/openclaw.json')));\nconst PROVIDERS_CONFIG = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(path.join(HOME, '.openclaw/config/providers.json')));\n\n// 初始化 ai-router\nconst aiRouter = new AIRouter({\n  providers: PROVIDERS_CONFIG.providers,\n  strategy: 'rate-limit-aware'\n});\n\n// 分类器缓存\nconst classifyCache = new NodeCache({ stdTTL: parseInt(process.env.CLASSIFIER_CACHE_TTL) || 300 });\n\n// ==================== 日志工具 ====================\nconst log = (level, msg, data = {}) => {\n  console.log(JSON.stringify({ level, ts: new Date().toISOString(), msg, ...data }));\n};\n\n// ==================== 路由决策 ====================\nfunction getModelConfig(agentId) {\n  const agent = (OPENCLAW_CONFIG.agents?.list || []).find(a => a.id === agentId);\n  const modelRef = agent?.modelRef || 'fast';\n  const modelConfig = MODELS_CONFIG.models[modelRef];\n  if (!modelConfig) throw new Error(`Model ref '${modelRef}' not found`);\n  return { modelRef, modelConfig };\n}\n\nfunction routeAgent(userMessage, classifierResult = null) {\n  const rules = [...RULES_CONFIG.rules].sort((a, b) => b.priority - a.priority);\n  \n  // 阶段1：关键词（优先级 ≥ 100）\n  for (const rule of rules) {\n    if (rule.priority < 100) continue;\n    if (rule.condition.always) continue;\n    if (rule.condition.contains) {\n      const matched = rule.condition.contains.some(kw => userMessage.includes(kw));\n      if (matched) {\n        const { modelConfig } = getModelConfig(rule.target_agent);\n        log('info', 'Route by keyword', { rule: rule.id, agent: rule.target_agent, model: modelConfig.modelId });\n        return { agentId: rule.target_agent, by: 'keyword' };\n      }\n    }\n  }\n  \n  // 阶段2：分类器标签\n\n[195 more lines in file. Use offset=61 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776176931503}}
{"type":"message","id":"168857b9","parentId":"29673b13","timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:28:51.526Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c5d073f31692444baa666a92","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"require('dotenv').config();\nconst express = require('express');\nconst fs = require('fs').promises;\nconst path = require('path');\nconst axios = require('axios');\nconst pino = require('pino');\n\nconst app = express();\napp.use(express.json());\n\n// 配置\nconst PORT = process.env.PORT || 3101;\nconst LLM_API_URL = process.env.LLM_API_URL || 'http://localhost:11434/api/generate';\nconst LLM_MODEL = process.env.LLM_MODEL || 'qwen2.5:7b';\nconst LLM_TIMEOUT = parseInt(process.env.LLM_TIMEOUT) || 30000;\nconst MAX_TOKENS = parseInt(process.env.MAX_CONTEXT_TOKENS) || 128000;\nconst THRESHOLD = parseFloat(process.env.COMPRESSION_THRESHOLD) || 0.8;\nconst MIN_MESSAGES = parseInt(process.env.MIN_MESSAGES_BEFORE_COMPRESS) || 6;\nconst KEEP_RECENT = parseInt(process.env.KEEP_RECENT_MESSAGES) || 5;\nconst MEMORY_DIR = process.env.MEMORY_DIR || './memory';\n\n// 日志\nconst logger = pino({\n level: process.env.LOG_LEVEL || 'info'\n \n});\n\n// 运行时状态\nlet sessionMessages = [];\nlet sessionId = 'default';\nlet lastSummary = '';\nlet compressionCount = 0;\nconst metrics = { requests: 0, compressions: 0, llmFailures: 0 };\n\n// 确保存储目录存在\nfs.mkdir(MEMORY_DIR, { recursive: true }).catch(e => logger.error(e, 'Failed to create memory dir'));\n\n// 加载最近一次会话快照（可选）\nasync function loadLatestSnapshot() {\n try {\n const files = await fs.readdir(MEMORY_DIR);\n const snapshots = files.filter(f => f.endsWith('.json')).sort().reverse();\n if (snapshots.length > 0) {\n const data = await fs.readFile(path.join(MEMORY_DIR, snapshots[0]), 'utf-8');\n const snapshot = JSON.parse(data);\n sessionMessages = snapshot.messages || [];\n lastSummary = snapshot.summary || '';\n sessionId = snapshot.sessionId || 'default';\n logger.info({ sessionId, messageCount: sessionMessages.length }, 'Loaded latest snapshot');\n }\n } catch (err) {\n logger.warn(err, 'No snapshot loaded, starting fresh');\n }\n}\n\n// Token 估算 (1 token ≈ 4 chars)\nfunction estimateTokens(text) {\n return Math.ceil(text.length / 4);\n}\n\n\n[182 more lines in file. Use offset=61 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776176931514}}
{"type":"message","id":"c77e2f3e","parentId":"168857b9","timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:29:01.783Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so both `proxy/index.js` and `context-api/index.js` are HTTP servers running on 3101 (context-api) and some other port (proxy), but neither is the main gateway. Let me check what ports are actually listening.\n\nActually, looking at the process list output again - `openclaw-gateway` is the main process (pid 433541). The proxy/index.js and context-api are separate services.\n\nLet me focus on what actually matters:1. The session-summary hook is configured in `hooks.internal.entries.session-summary`\n2. It listens for `type === \"command\" && (action === \"new\" || action === \"reset\")`3. The hook IS enabled\n\nBut the question is: what event type does the gateway actually emit for a `/new` command? Is it `command` or something else?\n\nLooking at the session-summary hook more carefully, I see it uses `extractMessages` to read from `.jsonl` session files. For webchat sessions, it would try to find session files in `agents/main/sessions/`. But the ephemeral directory is empty.\n\nWait - the ephemeral dir shows 0 files. But the context.json showed classification/scoring data was injected from the auto-score-classify hook. So the hooks ARE running.\n\nActually wait - the ephemeral dir is at `~/.openclaw/memory/ephemeral/` but the session-summary handler uses `path.join(MEMORY_DIR, \"ephemeral\")` where `MEMORY_DIR = ~/.openclaw/workspace/main/memory`. Let me check if that's different from `~/.openclaw/memory/ephemeral/`.\n\nThe handler.js sets `MEMORY_DIR = path.join(process.env.OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE_DIR || path.join(os.homedir(), \".openclaw\", \"workspace\"), \"memory\")`. So `~/.openclaw/workspace/main/memory/ephemeral`. But the auto-score-classify might write to `~/.openclaw/memory/ephemeral/`. These could be different directories.\n\n\nI need to figure out where auto-score-classify actually writes to, then trace whether the session-summary hook's event type even matches what the gateway emits.","thinkingSignature":"b5cc543299393191f88635343712471ab3c4b9f202cccc687149a51b1a6b6fdc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d320edd0ef844b5e96f539a9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/hooks/auto-score-classify/handler.js 2>/dev/null | grep -A5 \"ephemeral\\|writeFile\\|jsonl\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d987834359e241fc949c5a1f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/main/memory/ 2>/dev/null; ls ~/.openclaw/memory/ 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1282,"output":550,"cacheRead":43008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44840,"cost":{"input":0.00038459999999999997,"output":0.00066,"cacheRead":0.0025804799999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0036250799999999993}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776176931528,"responseId":"062d82235a97e25bf54c43374d8ff134"}}
