{"type":"message","id":"62ce77e1","parentId":"9a117c46","timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:30:16.909Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting - session-memory, session-summary, etc. are NOT registered in the loader. So these hooks are loaded externally (workspace hooks), not as internal hooks. The internal hooks system seems to be for built-in handlers.\n\nLet me look at the commands-reset-hooks file since it was mentioned earlier as calling `createInternalHookEvent` and `triggerInternalHook`.","thinkingSignature":"6149abcbe8c1348c14d0c2a377d2c2f85fd7a47613a44ad5b35d034c71666437"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8f5ad49cc35b48d0a5a95050","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/commands-reset-hooks-B7jYf1QC.js 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":245,"output":136,"cacheRead":50688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51069,"cost":{"input":0.0000735,"output":0.00016319999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00304128,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0032779799999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776177010628,"responseId":"062d827246c8954a3d4e17cffd39de4f"}}
