{"type":"message","id":"1b51aa18","parentId":"d9d8d3b3","timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:32:22.363Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I notice the commands.log is the only log file, and there's no gateway.log. The gateway logs go somewhere else or not at all.\n\nLet me approach this from a completely different angle. The `server.impl-BxLfE9ri.js` is the main server file. Let me look at how the `session_start` hook event is triggered when `/new` is executed. The `session-start` event emission should happen in `manager-vTWIfqhx.js`.\n\nActually wait - let me re-check. In `session-updates-BU9ULY8h.js`, I see:\n```js\nif (hookRunner.hasHooks(\"session_start\")) {\n    const payload = buildSessionStartHookPayload({...});\n    hookRunner.runSessionStart(payload.event, payload.context).catch(...);\n}\n```\n\nAnd `buildSessionStartHookPayload` returns an event with `sessionId`, `sessionKey`, `resumedFrom`. This event is passed to `runSessionStart` which calls `runVoidHook(\"session_start\", event, ctx)`.\n\nNow, `runVoidHook` calls `getHooksForName(registry, \"session_start\")` and runs each handler. The handlers were registered via `registerHook` during plugin loading.\n\nSo the question is: was the `memory-bootstrap` plugin's `session_start` hook registered during gateway startup?\n\nThis depends on whether the memory-bootstrap skill was properly installed and recognized as a plugin with a `session_start` hook.\n\nLet me check how the memory-bootstrap skill registers its hooks.","thinkingSignature":"f9064185662ef0e1c5305d6ae91f52cc9e8c26e9126062857ad4c6ee520d79ab"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f81d0c7f55e8428fb563c439","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/skills/memory-bootstrap/ 2>/dev/null; find ~/.openclaw/skills/memory-bootstrap -name \"*.json\" -o -name \"hook.json\" 2>/dev/null | head -5"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_02d6d6ec875149db968841f6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/skills/memory-bootstrap/hooks/openclaw/handler.js 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":233,"output":427,"cacheRead":70912,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71572,"cost":{"input":0.00006989999999999999,"output":0.0005124,"cacheRead":0.00425472,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00483702}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776177131259,"responseId":"062d82ebdaa243208c7c8cbc205d6a3b"}}
