ns type correction\n  - `wiki-learn-once.sh`: blocklist exact match fix\n  - `session-summary`: added `pruneOldSummaries(30天)` function\n  - `ephemeral isMeaningful`: duration>=2 condition preserved\n\n## Decisions\n- **Session is fresh**: No context.json or session-summary found for current session\n\n## Open TODOs\n- [ ] Verify session-summary bootstrap injection chain\n- [ ] Fix bootstrap-context timing (event fires after first reply)\n- [ ] Confirm wiki-auto-learn existence\n- [ ] Decide on openclaw-router (3101 context-api) retention\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- Session startup requires: read SOUL.md, USER.md, memory files, context.json, session-summary\n\n## Pending user asks\n- User's question: \"that chain run through?\" (referring to session-summary bootstrap injection chain)\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- Memory file: `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main/memory/2026-04-13.md`\n- Session context path: `~/.openclaw/sessions/main@*/context.json`\n- Scene classifier ports: 3105 (current), 3104 (deprecated)\n- Scorer port: 3103\n- Context-api (openclaw-router): port 3101, pid 434\n- Session-summary prune threshold: 30 days\n- Ephemeral meaningful condition: `duration>=2`\n- User's pending question: \"that chain run through?\"\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n\n\n## Decisions\n- **Event type mismatch**: `session-summary` hook checks `event.type === \"command\" && (action === \"new\" || \"reset\")`, while `handler.ts` (bootstrap) checks `event.type === \"agent\" && action === \"bootstrap\"` — different event types entirely.\n- **Webchat has no .jsonl session files**: `resolveSessionFile` returns null for webchat sessions because they store data in the gateway DB, not in `agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl`. The hook code tries to read session files but gets empty content.\n- **Ephemeral directory empty**: `/home/ai/.openclaw/memory/ephemeral/` has 0 lines across all `.jsonl` files (different path from hook's `~workspace/main/memory/ephemeral/`).\n\n## Open TODOs\n- Verify if `session-summary` hook actually fires on webchat `/new` commands (event type may never match)\n- Fix `resolveSessionFile` to retrieve webchat session content from DB instead of missing `.jsonl` files\n- Confirm `auto-score-classify` ephemeral output path vs `session-summary` ephemeral input path alignment\n- Check why ephemeral capture produced 0 entries (meaningful pattern filter may be too strict)\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- Session-summary hook must not error out — LLM failure falls back to rule-based summary silently\n- Bootstrap hook injects to `event.context.bootstrapFiles` array on `agent:bootstrap` events\n- Internal hooks enabled in `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` under `hooks.internal.entries` (all 6 entries enabled)\n\n## Pending user asks\n- User issued `深入查` (\"dig deeper\") — investigation is ongoing\n- Original context: bootstrap→session-summary injection chain is broken; session-summary file not found when new session starts\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- Hook config path: `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` → `hooks.internal.entries`\n- Hooks directory: `/home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/`\n- Bootstrap hook: `/home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/handler.js` / `handler.ts` — fires on `agent:bootstrap`\n- Session-summary hook: `/home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/handler.js` — fires on `command new/reset`\n- Session file path search order: `context.previousSessionEntry.sessionFile` → `context.sessionEntry.sessionFile` → `agents/main/sessions/`\n- Memory directory: `~/.openclaw/workspace/main/memory/` (MEMORY_DIR) vs `~/.openclaw/memory/` (separate location)\n- Ephemeral dir (session-summary reads from): `~/.openclaw/workspace/main/memory/ephemeral/` (empty — 0 lines)\n- Agent process: pid `433541`, binary `openclaw-gateway`\n- Session log: `~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/` — `.jsonl` files exist but webchat sessions use DB instead\n- Commands log: `~/.openclaw/logs/commands.log` — shows `{\"action\":\"new\", \"sessionKey\":\"agent:main:main\", \"senderId\":\"openclaw-control-ui\