{"type":"message","id":"1987f67e","parentId":"c6438420","timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:39:51.303Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see it clearly. The `emitResetCommandHooks` function calls `createInternalHookEvent(\"command\", params.action, ...)` where `action` is `\"new\"` or `\"reset\"`. So the event is `command:new` or `command:reset`.\n\nNow let me verify the hook loading to understand why the session-summary hook might not be running.\n\nLooking at the hook loading code, hooks are loaded from:\n1. `extraDirs` - from config\n2. `bundledHooksDir` - from openclaw dist\n3. `pluginHookDirs` - from plugins\n4. `managedHooksDir` (~/.openclaw/hooks)\n5. `workspaceHooksDir` (<workspace>/hooks)\n\nThe session-summary hook is at `~/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/` which is the managed hooks dir. The HOOK.md metadata says events: `[\"command:new\", \"command:reset\"]`.\n\nSo when the gateway starts, it should:\n1. Load all hooks from the managed dir\n2. Register `command:new` and `command:reset` for session-summary hook\n3. When `/new` is fired, `emitResetCommandHooks` triggers `command:new`\n4. The hook handler runs\n\nBut it's NOT working. Let me think about what could go wrong...\n\nWait - looking at the openclaw.json config:\n```json\n\"session-summary\": {\n    \"enabled\": true\n}\n```\n\nThe `enabled: true` should pass `shouldIncludeHook`. Let me check what shouldIncludeHook actually checks.\n\nFrom config-BAAmv8_d.js:120:\n```js\nfunction shouldIncludeHook(params) {\n```\n\nLet me look at this function.","thinkingSignature":"39e884b7f7c191d576cb0e92a9542c9b0fced092d7c4aeba972f54ca9f4954b2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fdfe40aa69b0411d802db9ee","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '115,145p' ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/config-BAAmv8_d.js 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1182,"output":412,"cacheRead":60288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61882,"cost":{"input":0.0003546,"output":0.0004944,"cacheRead":0.0036172799999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0044662799999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776177583441,"responseId":"062d84aeed7cc19f7a28607698dc51b8"}}
