{"type":"message","id":"12de851a","parentId":"a7c1ea75","timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:42:15.280Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me take a step back and think about this. I need to verify whether the bootstrap chain is working. The issue is that we can't directly observe the gateway's hook loading. But we CAN observe the results - does the session-summary file get created after /new?\n\nLet me try a completely different approach - just trigger a /new and observe what happens. But wait, I'm in a webchat session. If I send /new, it will restart my session. Let me instead look at the existing session's ephemeral data and see if there's any indication that hooks ran.\n\nActually, let me think about this differently. The context.json shows classification/scoring data - this means the auto-score-classify hook IS running (or the v8 router is handling it). \n\nSo if auto-score-classify is working through the internal hooks mechanism, then session-summary should also be working through that same mechanism. Let me check if auto-score-classify is actually a bundled hook or something different.","thinkingSignature":"4590baa285f6ba966fb55f192d2243987b5eb2efb79fd501e725c7e89e9324fa"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f95bfc0d4b794d1986120a15","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/hooks/auto-score-classify/HOOK.md 2>/dev/null | head -30"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_15320d311cb841868ba13f33","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/hooks/auto-score-classify/handler.js 2>/dev/null | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":952,"output":286,"cacheRead":67648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68886,"cost":{"input":0.0002856,"output":0.0003432,"cacheRead":0.00405888,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00468768}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776177727175,"responseId":"062d853e690afad4b17d01fe338450c8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"81021914","parentId":"12de851a","timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:42:15.382Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f95bfc0d4b794d1986120a15","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: auto-score-classify\ndescription: \"每条消息自动调用 v8_classifier(3105) 和 v8_scorer(3103)，结果写入 session 状态文件供 agent 读取\"\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"emoji\": \"🎯\",\n        \"events\": [\"message:preprocessed\"],\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"node\"], \"config\": [] },\n        \"always\": true\n      }\n  }\n---\n\n# auto-score-classify\n\n每条入站消息自动经过意图分类 + 复杂度评分，结果写入 session 目录。\n\n## 结果文件\n\n`~/.openclaw/sessions/{sessionKey}/context.json`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"classification\": {\n    \"response\": \"[LLM响应] 基于你的输入，建议操作如下：...\",\n    \"intercepted\": false,\n    \"scene\": \"task_multi_step\",\n    \"meta\": \"confident\","}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":61,"aggregated":"---\nname: auto-score-classify\ndescription: \"每条消息自动调用 v8_classifier(3105) 和 v8_scorer(3103)，结果写入 session 状态文件供 agent 读取\"\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"emoji\": \"🎯\",\n        \"events\": [\"message:preprocessed\"],\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"node\"], \"config\": [] },\n        \"always\": true\n      }\n  }\n---\n\n# auto-score-classify\n\n每条入站消息自动经过意图分类 + 复杂度评分，结果写入 session 目录。\n\n## 结果文件\n\n`~/.openclaw/sessions/{sessionKey}/context.json`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"classification\": {\n    \"response\": \"[LLM响应] 基于你的输入，建议操作如下：...\",\n    \"intercepted\": false,\n    \"scene\": \"task_multi_step\",\n    \"meta\": \"confident\",","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776177735378}}
{"type":"message","id":"eddf8d73","parentId":"81021914","timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:42:15.389Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_15320d311cb841868ba13f33","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// auto-score-classify hook\n// Concurrent classification (3105) + scoring (3103) on every inbound message\n// + ephemeral memory capture for meaningful messages\n\nimport fs from \"node:fs\";\nimport path from \"node:path\";\nimport http from \"node:http\";\n\nasync function fetchJSON(url, body, timeoutMs = 3000) {\n  return new Promise((resolve) => {\n    const postData = JSON.stringify(body);\n    const req = http.request(\n      url,\n      {\n        method: \"POST\",\n        headers: { \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\", \"Content-Length\": Buffer.byteLength(postData) },\n      },\n      (res) => {\n        let data = \"\";\n        res.on(\"data\", (chunk) => (data += chunk));\n        res.on(\"end\", () => {\n          try { resolve(JSON.parse(data)); }\n          catch { resolve(null); }\n        });\n      }\n    );\n    req.on(\"error\", () => resolve(null));\n    req.setTimeout(timeoutMs, () => { req.destroy(); resolve(null); });\n    req.write(postData);\n    req.end();"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":68,"aggregated":"// auto-score-classify hook\n// Concurrent classification (3105) + scoring (3103) on every inbound message\n// + ephemeral memory capture for meaningful messages\n\nimport fs from \"node:fs\";\nimport path from \"node:path\";\nimport http from \"node:http\";\n\nasync function fetchJSON(url, body, timeoutMs = 3000) {\n  return new Promise((resolve) => {\n    const postData = JSON.stringify(body);\n    const req = http.request(\n      url,\n      {\n        method: \"POST\",\n        headers: { \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\", \"Content-Length\": Buffer.byteLength(postData) },\n      },\n      (res) => {\n        let data = \"\";\n        res.on(\"data\", (chunk) => (data += chunk))