{"type":"message","id":"b6cf6314","parentId":"a33a0ce6","timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:45:47.012Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me now provide a comprehensive summary of what I found. The key issue is that the gateway needs to be restarted to load the updated session-summary handler.\n","thinkingSignature":"c3f264fb578cfecd084efdbb8dbe28c4e978b3f734c712217a1205d6c0111cc0"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n[[reply_to_current]] 查完了。结论：\n\n**链路状态：部分跑通，需要重启 gateway 才能完全跑通。**\n\n---\n\n## 验证结果\n\n### ✅ 已跑通的部分\n- **3103/3105 微服务**：正常工作\n- **auto-score-classify hook**：正常触发（context.json 有数据）\n- **session-summary hook 代码**：逻辑正确，handler.js 已更新\n- **bootstrap hook 代码**：handler.js 已更新，逻辑正确\n\n### ❌ 未跑通的部分\n- **session-summary 文件未生成**：没有 `memory/*session-summary*.md` 文件\n- **PREVIOUS_SESSION_SUMMARY 未注入 bootstrap**：本次 session 的 SOUL.md 注入中没有看到上次的摘要\n\n---\n\n## 根本原因\n\n**gateway 启动于 Apr 14 19:30，但 session-summary handler.js 在 21:42 才修改。**\n\ngateway 启动时加载的旧版 session-summary handler 可能：\n1. 有 bug 导致静默失败\n2. 或者 hook 根本没被注册（旧版代码的 event filter 可能有问题）\n\n同样，handler.js（bootstrap hook）修改于 21:37，但 gateway 19:30 就启动了。\n\n---\n\n## 修复方案\n\n**重启 gateway**（二选一）：\n\n```bash\n# 方案1：graceful restart（推荐）\nkill -USR1 433541   # 向 gateway 发送重启信号\n\n# 方案2：full restart  \npkill openclaw-gateway; sleep 2; cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && openclaw gateway start &\n```\n\n重启后验证：\n```bash\n# 等待 10 秒后检查\nls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace/main/memory/*session-summary* 2>/dev/null\n```\n\n重启后下次 `/new` 时：\n1. `session-summary` hook 应该生成 `memory/2026-04-14-session-summary-*.md`\n2. bootstrap hook 读取该文件作为 PREVIOUS_SESSION_SUMMARY.md 注入\n\n---\n\n需要我执行重启吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":698,"output":454,"cacheRead":74688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75840,"cost":{"input":0.0002094,"output":0.0005448,"cacheRead":0.00448128,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00523548}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776177936208,"responseId":"062d860