{"type":"message","id":"f4eec047","parentId":"a43f7aed","timestamp":"2026-04-14T14:55:54.021Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The file was written to `~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/` (which is `~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/`) instead of `~/.openclaw/workspace/main/memory/`. \n\nThis means the MEMORY_DIR calculation in session-summary handler is wrong for our setup. It's using `~/.openclaw/workspace` instead of `~/.openclaw/workspace/main`.\n\nLet me check the handler code to see how MEMORY_DIR is calculated. From the handler.js:\n\n```javascript\nconst MEMORY_DIR = path.join(\n  process.env.OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE_DIR ||\n    path.join(os.homedir(), \".openclaw\", \"workspace\"),\n  \"memory\"\n\n\n);\n```\n\nThe issue is that `OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE_DIR` is either not set or points to `~/.openclaw/workspace` rather than `~/.openclaw/workspace/main`. When this env var isn't defined, the fallback constructs `~/.openclaw/workspace/memory`, but that's not where our memory files actually live.\n\nLooking at the bootstrap handler's MEMORY_DIR calculation, it also uses `process.env.OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE_DIR` with the same fallback, which would resolve to the same incorrect path if the env var isn't set. Both hooks are reading from and writing to `~/.openclaw/workspace/memory` when they should be using `~/.openclaw/workspace/main/memory` instead.\n\nThe bootstrap hook reads from `~/.openclaw/workspace/memory`, but our session summaries are actually in `~/.openclaw/workspace/main/memory/`. So even if the session-summary hook were generating files, they wouldn't be found by the bootstrap hook because they're in the wrong directory.\n\nThe root cause is that `OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE_DIR` is either not set or pointing to the wrong location. It should be `~/.openclaw/workspace/main` but appears to be set to `~/.openclaw/workspace` instead. I need to figure out where this environment variable is configured in the gateway startup script.","thinkingSignature":"f5dcb4175b41c9055b807d9677ddddbfe3ad1e733efc0479319cba8af103c79e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n找到 bug 了！文件写错位置了：\n\n```\n写入位置：~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-14-session-summary-无会话内容.md\n正确位置：~/.openclaw/workspace/main/memory/\n```\n\n问题：`OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE_DIR` 环境变量指向 `~/.openclaw/workspace` 而不是 `~/.openclaw/workspace/main`。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_52c2af51d8014d9b83b6406f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE_DIR=$OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE_DIR\"\ngrep -r \"OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE_DIR\" ~/.openclaw/ --include=\"*.sh\" --include=\"*.env*\" --include=\"*.service\" 2>/dev/null | head -10\nps aux | grep openclaw-gateway | grep -v grep"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":112,"output":583,"cacheRead":78272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78967,"cost":{"input":0.0000336,"output":0.0006996,"cacheRead":0.0046963199999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005429519999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776178544049,"responseId":"062d886f7b8f31edab1fc46ae7ab854f"}}
