{"type":"message","id":"2bfa780e","parentId":"b367413d","timestamp":"2026-04-14T15:04:23.206Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `session-summary` hook writes files with format `YYYY-MM-DD-session-summary-{slug}.md`. So the session-summary hook generates files with `-session-summary-` in the middle, not `-session-summary.md` at the end.\n\nBut wait - `endsWith('-session-summary.md')` checks for files ending with that exact string. Let me check what the session-summary hook actually produces:\n\n```\n2026-04-14-session-summary-无会话内容.md\n```\n\nThis ends with `.md`, not `-session-summary.md`. So the bootstrap hook's filter `f.endsWith('-session-summary.md')` would NOT match files generated by session-summary hook!\n \nAh, I see the issue now - session-summary creates files with the slug between the prefix and extension like `2026-04-14-session-summary-{slug}.md`, but bootstrap is filtering for files ending with `-session-summary.md` as a literal suffix. The session-summary hook should be checking for `*-session-summary-*.md` instead. I'm seeing the actual bug now—my grep filters for `endsWith('-session-summary.md')` but the session-summary hook generates files with a slug between \"session-summary\" and the extension, so those files would end in `.md` instead of that exact suffix. The test file I created has `session-summary-verify.md` which doesn't match the filter either, explaining why nothing's showing up.","thinkingSignature":"6740114bced1d6d588886d58af3a31c5b6a7d28f29d5ce216d018e59541ad145"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白了！`session-summary` hook 生成的文件格式是 `YYYY-MM-DD-session-summary-{slug}.md`（有 slug 在中间），但 bootstrap hook 过滤的是 `endsWith('-session-summary.md')`（无 slug）——**后缀不匹配**！\n\n这就是为什么 bootstrap hook 找不到任何 session-summary 文件。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1f2be6f90c4b412d9aa23bf8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"endsWith.*session.summary\\|filter.*session.summary\\|summaryFiles\" ~/.openclaw/hooks/handler.js 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":237,"output":408,"cacheRead":84800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85445,"cost":{"input":0.0000711,"output":0.0004896,"cacheRead":0.005088,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0056486999999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776179052937,"responseId":"062d8a6d4da792a08c6639400d80f86e"}}
