{"type":"message","id":"a4aa2d2c","parentId":"55dfda05","timestamp":"2026-04-14T15:04:34.674Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is clear now:1. `session-summary` hook writes: `2026-04-14-session-summary-{slug}.md`\n2. `bootstrap handler.js` filters: `f.endsWith('-session-summary.md')`The files look like:- `2026-04-14-session-summary-无会话内容.md`\n- `2026-04-14-session-summary-assistant.md`\n- `2026-04-14-session-summary-verify.md`These all contain `-session-summary-` in the middle, not ending with `-session-summary.md`.Wait actually:- `2026-04-14-session-summary-无会话内容.md` - does this end with `-session-summary.md`? Let's check:  - The string is `2026-04-14-session-summary-无会话内容.md`  - Does it end with `-session-summary.md`? NO! It ends with `.md` but before that is `-无会话内容.md`  - So `endsWith('-session-summary.md')` is FALSE- What about a file like `2026-04-14-session-summary.md` (hypothetical)?  - This would end with `-session-summary.md` ✓So the session-summary hook generates files with a slug between `summary` and `.md`, but the bootstrap filter expects no slug.I need to fix the filter in handler.js to match files that contain `-session-summary-` (with the hyphen after summary).Files like:- `2026-04-14-session-summary-无会话内容.md`- `2026-04-14-session-summary-assistant.md`Should match using: `f.includes('-session-summary-')`\n","thinkingSignature":"64be864a0e718bcfe3201cad3a8735e904983684a8bdee65ebf74d7b5394cdf7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n确认了！问题在 `handler.js` 第 45 行：\n\n```javascript\nconst summaryFiles = files.filter(f => f.endsWith('-session-summary.md'));\n```\n\n但实际文件名是：\n- `2026-04-14-session-summary-无会话内容.md`\n- `2026-04-14-session-summary-assistant.md`\n\n这些包含 `-session-summary-`（中间有 slug），不匹配 `endsWith('-session-summary.md')`。\n\n修复过滤逻辑：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e2c74be14fda496f833efb0c","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    const summaryFiles = files.filter(f => f.includes('-session-summary-') && f.endsWith('.md'));","oldText":"    const summaryFiles = files.filter(f => f.endsWith('-session-summary.md'));"}],"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/handler.js"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":225,"output":537,"cacheRead":84992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85754,"cost":{"input":0.0000675,"output":0.0006443999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00509952,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005811419999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776179063310,"responseId":"062d8a77a8b8c973a8f8356ec5b38ac6"}}
